cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about communication-efficient distributed deep learning algorithms, which involves topics such as machine learning (cs.LG), distributed computing (cs.DC), parallel computing (cs.DS), system design (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper covers a wide range of topics related to distributed deep learning, including system-level and algorithmic-level optimizations, communication synchronization, system architectures, compression techniques, and parallelism of communication and computing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, and cs.CV.
